      "content": "everything is just slipping away. the doctors keep talking about \"management\" and \"coping\" but it feels like i'm just waiting to become a ghost in my own house. i used to be so independent. now i cant even tie my own shoes without help. is there any dignity left when you aren't the one in control anymore?",
